Legacy note:

This file was inherited from IAMR-era documentation instructions and is no
longer the authoritative workflow for this repository.

For iLBMReX docs:

1. Edit Markdown docs under `Docs/Docs/`.
2. Edit Sphinx sources under:
   - `Docs/Docs/sphinx_documentation/source/`
   - `Docs/Docs/iLBMReX_documentation/source/`
3. Build locally from the corresponding Sphinx directory with `make html`
   (or `make latexpdf` if LaTeX dependencies are installed).
